dct_alternative_sm: Nieuwe Pascaert van de Oost Zee
dct_description_sm: Decorative cartouche (with figures), compass roses, rhumb lines, ships.
Shows water depths, shoals, rocks, anchorages, ports.
Dutch throughout, including translation of title and scale statements.
Appears in Renard's Atlas de la navigation, et du commerce qui se fait dans toutes les parties du monde, Amsterdam : R. und J. Ottens, 1739.
